en-US.title: Howard Brown Health Halsted
en-US.description: An inclusive health center providing a variety of services focused on the needs of the transgender community. Services include trans and non-binary health, men's health, women's health, pediatric services, geriatric medicine, HIV services, dental services, counseling and support, and sexual and reproductive health. Committed to an informed-consent approach to healthcare.

address: 3245 N Halsted St, Chicago, IL 60657, USA
